subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)

lead_paragraph: Senior point guard Eric Maynor will help make the 11th-seeded Rams a popular choice to pull off a first-round upset in the N.C.A.A. tournament when they face sixth-seeded U.C.L.A.
